{"tid":2425925,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林書豪透露被稱「冠狀病毒」 NBA發展聯盟展開調查","createTime":"2021-02-27T16:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T17:22:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ff9c7dd95507c3287ea561c7c7f02da41f6a1e","tid":2425925,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"美籍華裔籃球員林書豪透露自己在球場上被人稱作「冠狀病毒」，NBA發展聯盟表示會展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n林書豪在社交網站發文，指新一代亞裔美國人厭倦社會聲稱沒有種族主義，亦厭倦被告知要保持低調、不要製造麻煩。他稱即使自己有9年NBA經驗，仍在場上被人稱作「冠狀病毒」，但他沒有透露事發詳情，他希望藉此為受歧視的亞裔美國人發聲。<br />\n<br />\n林書豪現時效力NBA發展聯盟球隊聖克魯斯勇士，發展聯盟發聲明稱會調查事件，球隊教練則表示支持林書豪。<br />\n<br />\n32歲的林書豪早年效力過多支NBA球隊，之後轉戰過CBA，早前加盟NBA發展聯盟，為重返NBA鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425574&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm5Fs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=235dcc68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425574&h=ea940262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425574</a>"},{"pid":"6d99a82c08fc986da75e12d4bc1ca1fbad6806d5","tid":2425925,"uid":101481,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"又唔畀叫 china virus  咁你想叫咩啫"},{"pid":"75a41db976cc563245e700a962a3380d162223e3","tid":2425925,"uid":364068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:11:06.000Z","msg":"武肺豪"},{"pid":"c8a8a5730e6584cc756316740698cc7f1c0f5dca","tid":2425925,"uid":28309,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"啲nigga成日話black live matter<br />\n人地live就唔matter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9219aa22df8fa224f67354a9c028cc5b71e002f0","tid":2425925,"uid":4322,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score